Pivotal HDB on Hortonworks HDP Sandbox
--------------------------------------

This release only works for the vmware version.
* Download the VMWARE version of Sandbox 2.4
* Import into Fusion
* Boot Sandbox
* Change root password
* Note the root password in the packer json file
* Change path to VMX in packer json
* Put HDB and PLugin Binary in ./bins/
* Build
